那么得到的是<i>a</i>^<i>x</i>/Log[<i>a</i>]

80
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:30,000
Okay. Let’s go a step deeper into the number <i>e</i>.
好 让我们进一步了解这个数字 <i>e</i>

